  "detailed_description": "Kuggs is a fast-paced shooter with some light horror elements. <br>Fight off hordes of enemies and grow stronger over 70 levels. Can you defeat all of the bosses?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966310/extras/7ba61b0c856b1db235e430b8e4ceb168.poster.avif?t=1685065879\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966310/extras/7ba61b0c856b1db235e430b8e4ceb168.webm?t=1685065879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1966310/extras/7ba61b0c856b1db235e430b8e4ceb168.mp4?t=1685065879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun Mechanics</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique Art Style</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Challenging Gameplay</li></ul><strong><br>-Choose your powerup (speed bonus, orb magnet, double ammo) <br>-Choose your bullet type (fire, frost, poison)<br>-Collect orbs to gain experience<br>-Level 1-70</strong><br><br><strong>Controls : <br>A - Left<br>D - Right<br>Space - boost upwards<br>Hold left mouse to fire.<br>R- return to main room <br>P- restart game<br>Esc - Exit</strong><br><br><br>*menu under construction, take note of controls*",
